Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:06.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:19.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition \N- in which a winner will get the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Flare-Flare Fruit as the prize \N- and won the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:33.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but now, he's heading for the palace\Nto take back Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who's been captured by Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, underground Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:42.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp and the others started the \Noperation to take down Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tail Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe we can pull it off\Nwithout me fighting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys!\NI, Usoland, am taking command now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go frighten her out of her wits!\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lead the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the Executive Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze! I'm taking over this lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna learn to fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain and wind will rust my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you doing this?!\NYou're just a toy, what do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a peaceful country where...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my child can live happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take Dressrosa back\Nfor the King Riku Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!\NEverybody's collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened in a blink of an eye,\Nin the Block D match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody is about to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The End of the Match?!\NA Surprising Result of Block D!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very bizarre ending for a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 20-some surviving tough \Nfighters have suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been knocked out for an unknown reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never happened before\Nin the long history of the Corrida Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the center of the ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can see the shadow of someone\Nwho is struggling to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the winner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That person of the shadow has done all this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rebecca who just stood to her feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The well-known warriors who we thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would dominate the Block D match,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all still lying down on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Corrida Colosseum Battle Tournament -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the last winner moving to the finals is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unbelievably, a convict gladiator \Nand a granddaughter of King Riku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blot in the history of Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Screw you!\N--I know she cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trick did you use, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cloud of dust enveloped the ring\Nall of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!\NIn any event, Rebecca has won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!\NWhat did she do to Cavendish-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Orlumbus couldn't be \Nbeaten by such a little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was The Slicing Winds of Rommel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slicing Winds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NI bet you've never heard of it-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mysterious incident\Nthat took place in the Rommel Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say winds that cut people \Nblew there every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhat a bizarre story-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dispatched the Navy soldiers right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:09:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the winds killed a lot of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing they found \Nout at the end was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the wind was actually a man\Nwho called himself Hakuba-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is still at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he left the Rommel Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba kept terrorizing \Npeople in various towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wherever Hakuba appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this pirate is always there \Nat the same time-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me!\NYou little bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's acting strange!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a sleepwalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuba is, indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an alter-ego of Cavendish\Nthat awakens while he is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hakuba committed a crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NCavendish had no choice but set out to the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became a pirate-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel sorry for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's enjoying the situation!\NHe'd take advantage of your sympathies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a great swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hakuba is far stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, he falls asleep\Nwhen his alter-ego appears
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that nature wasn't suitable \Nfor a battle royal, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rebecca can't be a winner!\N--I'm sure she used a pistol or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check her out already and eliminate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we inspect Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always check her\Nmore strictly than the regulations demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her equipment is the poorest\Namong all the competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Corrida Colosseum,\Nthe winner is the winner no matter who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our job to manipulate the facts\Nand spoil someone's victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won without landing a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way to win a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she wasn't just lucky -\Nshe was the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who fended off Hakuba's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see anything!\NOnly you my great {\i1}senpai{\i0} could see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it is, though,\NI can't let anybody have the Flare-Flare Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait any longer!\NI can finally fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the finals next!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool! He's totally messing around with\Nthat mechanical guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor! Just kick that geek's ass already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor girls don't get \Nhow cool cyborgs are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how pretty my mechanical body is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't get it at all!\NWhat's so cool about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Señor's look is\Nten-thousand times prettier than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the way a man is,\Nyou immature flappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way a man is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pacifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this drool bib!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wearing them to attract you tramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my style and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it represents the way I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of like the way you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am a man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got to take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:52.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:57.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SUIT CHAMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your granddaughter sure is lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to enter the competition\Nalong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, King Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a man who was once a king\Nfought for the Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're quite desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the members of your family are\Ngoing too far today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was also Violet's betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's too much to be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of anniversary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're not aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you did this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the report on Doflamingo's abdication
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the throne and the Seven Warlords \Nthat spread all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake. Just a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I learned that the slight hope was\Njust a hoax,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it made me want to fight for everything\Nin this country again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That was why you made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Viola was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, she is a calculating tramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll never act purely on her emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's weighing her options.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is this top rookie\Nwho came to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there is someone who has \Ndemonic blood in his veins
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and grabbed all the limelight two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch is wishing those two \Nallied pirates will defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Law is barely alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Straw Hat Luffy will never come \Nout of the Colosseum as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, as for the other \Nmembers of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyborg Franky is attacking the Toy House\Non his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think he can beat\Nthe executives of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest - Pirate Hunter Zoro,\NFoxfire Kin'emon, Nico Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Sniperking are still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think they can even reach\Nthe underground level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hello, sir!\N--Oh! New recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you! The job here is easy -\Nyou just push around the toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? That's good to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about this place\Nso can you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:30.79,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,AT THE FOOT OF THE "KING'S PLATEAU"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lift up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:36.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LUFFY IN A CARP SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ZORO IN A CAT SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KIN'EMON IN A FROG SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.23,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palace where Doflamingo \Nis and the Toy House
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:49.51,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Toy House
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the trade port where the \NSMILE factory are located -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:51.81,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palace\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Toy House\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NThe Trade Port
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthey are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, if we can get into the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe can go to the Toy House and the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To go to the factory, \Nyou have to pass through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Neither the palace or the Toy House.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my colleagues must've \Nsnuck into the trade port
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthrough the secret passage that we dug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go to the palace first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't get over how
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are such small people\Neven though I see one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she looks like a toy!\NHow interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were tons of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Let me meet them later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't do this often!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only show ourselves\Nto the Big Humans of the royal family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you Usolanders, aka the Straw Hats,\Nare the exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usolanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain everything later!\NOperation SOP is already underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:22:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the lift to the \Nentrance of the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go that high with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To enter the lift, we have to show a pass\Nto a security guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do such a thing, it's gonna be messy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand we'll have to face more enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bubblehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to the blockhead who gets lost easily,\NI'm with a witless bubblehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call a blockhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is somebody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They already know that we're here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Straw Hat Luffy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'll help you enter to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
